up Calvary's Mountain ♪

16:37.800 --> 16:43.534
♪ One day they nailed him
to die on a tree ♪

16:43.714 --> 16:49.847
♪ suffering anguish,
despised and rejected ♪

16:50.003 --> 16:55.362
♪ bearing our sins,
my redeemer is he ♪

16:55.550 --> 16:58.557
♪ the hand that healed nations ♪
[ cellphone vibrates ]

16:58.605 --> 17:01.445
♪ stretched out on a tree ♪
[ cellphone vibrates ]

17:01.651 --> 17:04.847
[ vibrating stops ]
